  "articleContent": "<div><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1778256000000/eaa42n5mgjnvzc7t5l-1778308825476.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\">\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">Her name, her identity, her Resonance Ability, even the ties she claimed to others... all of it was a lie.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">Between you and the Keystone stands nothing more but a puppet who came into existence only because of Aleph-1.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1778256000000/fbb1hhm868wz9j4bll-1778308878900.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"2962\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1778256000000/av9awgqpx0183hojb9-1778308895109.gif\" width=\"800\" height=\"1167\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1778256000000/au2wlnng0x5cx9msfr-1778308904966.gif\" width=\"800\" height=\"1167\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1778256000000/hoz0xhqza1vog9oghm-1778308913684.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"1909\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-